headline: Fiserv Stock Hit A Record High In March. With Market On The Upswing, Can It Do It Again?
summary: Financial services company Fiserv reported underwhelming earnings a week ago, on April 24, and its stock fell.  The upgraded RS rating shows that Fiserv tops 72% of all other stocks for price performance this past year.  Fiserv has a terrific 91 Composite Rating out of 99.
